dct_title_s: Map to accompany notes of a journey through Manchuria by the Archimandrite Palladius
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Settlements along route and major rivers are shown. Great Wall of China and palisade are shown. Distances given in English miles, geographical miles, Russian versts, and Chinese li. From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 42 (1872), pp. 142-80; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.42 1872
